title: Kabu Sky v1.0.0.3 [Android] [.apk]
description:
Fly on the balloon and rescue your love! Be the bravest of all sheeps. Fight as sheep Kabu and defeat the evil Dino.

Kabu Sky is free fascinating 2D platformer game. It combines "shoot and fly" and platformer game in one. Everything you ever loved - varied enemies , collectables, cool weapons and lots more!

World 1 - Deep Forest - contains 20 exciting levels full of collectable items and bonuses. 

Features:

- Exciting game play
- Realistic phisics
- Hero customization
- Epic boss fights
- Cool weapons
- 20 levels on every world
